Class GetElements

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.Contextualizable, Cloneable

    public class GetElements
extends ca.uqac.lif.cep.functions.UnaryFunction<Multiset,Multiset>
    Gets all the elements of the multiset that satisfy some condition. This condition is specified as an unary function that is successively applied to each element of the multiset; if the function returns true, the element is added to the output result, otherwise it is discarded.
